-- Egypt's EFG-Hermes Holding Unit Gets Investment Banking License in Syria
-- Alaa Shahine
-- 2010-04-26T11:35:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/egypt-s-efg-hermes-holding-unit-gets-investment-banking-license-in-syria.html

          
          
             EFG-Hermes Holding SAE said today
Syrian authorities granted its unit in the Arab country licenses
for full advisory and corporate finance, research, securities
brokerage and asset management.  
 The Cairo-based investment bank made the announcement in a
statement distributed by the Regulatory News Service.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
